            "body": "When you remove `noplainbuffer`, you're telling Neovim to spellcheck all text, and not the regions that treesitter specifies.\r\n\r\nYou can check if a node is marked for spellchecking by placing your cursor over some text and running `:Inspect` and check if it includes a `@spell` capture.",
